Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:46.60,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这份心情  一定会消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.77,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}旋转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:52.56,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}持有着这魔法之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:55.69,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}眼泪与Sunny day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:58.15,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)\blur3}溶于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:02.24,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}寂寞的人的身旁
